column5: Good morning Lew, nice shot.  No sign of sunshine here this morning, yet.
Sunshine only lasted 10 minutes here Chris, now it's clouded over again. Good thing I looked out the window when I did
Maybe I should go outside and wait and see if I can catch 10 minutes of sun.
Come here! We've had sun for the last half hour.
Got the boat hooked up and heading to pre fish the derby on the river, going to be sunny when I put the first Walter in the net  Sheephead in the net, cloudy Happy Thanks Giving boys.
Bluebird skies here in Montreal. A chil in the air though.2C last nite.Happy Thanksgiving all.
Morning Lew.  Chilly and raining lightly here  Walleye time with the kids, after one more cup of coffee of course
Hey Lew, get the firehose out.  Your trees are on fire!  Nice
Nice Photo Lew! Thanks for that!
